{"body": "> .yardoc\r\n\r\nGood point.\r\n\r\n> test/tmp\r\n\r\nAgreed, if test libraries are shoving into test/tmp they should be told to push to tmp/test to be more obvious.\r\n\r\n> .svn/, secret_token.rb, and *.yml\r\n\r\nPerhaps these could be in a commented out \"Commonly added\" section, with some notes on why you want to ignore secret_token and database.yml.\r\n\r\nI see all too many rails applications who don't do this, and it ends up biting them in the ass.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/2910130", "created_at": "2011-11-29T00:34:36Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/3777#issuecomment-2910130", "updated_at": "2011-11-29T00:34:36Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 3777, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/krainboltgreene/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/krainboltgreene/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/krainboltgreene/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/krainboltgreene", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/krainboltgreene/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/krainboltgreene", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/krainboltgreene/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/15d21696a56b183503cf2c82114be9d6?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F621565b35926d1e7fcfa1f5a8b3740e6.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/krainboltgreene/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/krainboltgreene/received_events", "gravatar_id": "15d21696a56b183503cf2c82114be9d6", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/krainboltgreene/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "krainboltgreene", "type": "User", "id": 334809, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/krainboltgreene/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523831c8bd3543c15100f7eb"}, "id": 2910130, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/3777"}
